            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Open Houses</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Organize and host open houses to attract potential buyers and maximize exposure.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Negotiation Skills</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Skillful negotiation to achieve the best price and terms for your property.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Additional Services</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Investment Properties</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Specialized services for investors seeking profitable real estate opportunities.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Property Management</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Comprehensive management services to handle rental properties efficiently.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Relocation Assistance</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Guidance and support for individuals and families relocating to new areas.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 bg-gray-200 rounded-lg">
                <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Legal and Financial Advice</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-700">Access to expert advice on legal matters and financial implications of real estate transactions.</p>
            </div>
